50|$|Debris on the backstretch {{brought out}} the second caution of the race on lap 99. Keselowski and Logano swapped the lead on <b>pit</b> <b>road</b> with the former pitting before the start/finish line, but Jimmie Johnson exited <b>pit</b> <b>road</b> with the lead after taking just right-side tires.|$|R
